entity.name: Updates on the Covid-19 situation in the Philippines
entity.description: This page provides real-time updates on the Covid-19 situation from trusted and official sources.

text:
Duterte is set to decide today whether or not to extend the ECQ in Metro Manila and other areas with a large number of COVID-19 cases.

It will be the President’s third time to render a decision on the extension or lifting of the ECQ. https://t.co/SZa2umklDv
